      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/57/1182",
      "text": [
        "1182 - وَ قَدْ رُوِيَ: «أَنَّهُ إِنْ خَافَ عَلَى نَفْسِهِ مِنْ أَجْلِ مَنْ يُصَلِّي مَعَهُ صَلَّى اَلرَّكْعَتَيْنِ اَلْأَخِيرَتَيْنِ وَ جَعَلَهُمَا تَطَوُّعاً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1182 - It has been narrated: \"If a person fears for himself due to those praying with him, he should pray the last two rak'ahs and make them voluntary (nafl) prayers”."
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications"
